Entries.default: "Damn it, there's too many. We shouldn't go in without a plan."
"We should find a way around them. There is no reason to fight any more than we must."
"Who's in favor of the long way around?"
"What I wouldn't do for a mongoose right about now."
"Remaro had no end of tales bout the snake folk. Weren't a one of them ended happy."
"Ah... maybe another route, captain? One that does not take us into the snake's nest?"
